title: In case of composite development i
clause_text: In case of composite development i.e. the plot consisting of tenant occupied building along with non-tenanted building such as owner occupied building/existing Co-op Housing Society buildings etc., the FSI available shall be equal to FSI required for rehabilitation of existing lawful tenant plus 50% incentive FSI plus FSI that has already authorisedly been utilized/consumed by the non-tenanted buildings/structures.
section: 33(6) Reconstruction of buildings destroyed by fire or which have collapsed or which have been demolished under lawful order
